item.title: PRESS
item.description: NorCal Native Young King, born Miguel Angel Guevara, 22, is a multi-faceted recording artist, entrepreneur. Miguel (Young King) was raised in the sunny town of Willits, California where he was brought up on strong Catholic and Hispanic cultural values. Here and with his family, he fostered an early love of music. At a young age he joined school and community talent camps, and began to take to social media.
